      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Now in early access — start free, no card required</span>

      <h1>The <em>full feature stack</em><br />for your business</h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">
        Bookkeeping, payroll, business formation, PBX, ledger, finops,
        and AI CFO intelligence — unified in one platform. Start free, add only what you need.
      </p>

      <div class="feature-stack-grid">
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">📒</span> Bookkeeping</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">💰</span> Payroll</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">🏛️</span> BizForma</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">📞</span> PBX</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">📊</span> Ledger &amp; GL</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">🧾</span> Finance Ops</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">🤖</span> AI CFO</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">🔍</span> Scout CRM</span>
        <span class="fs-pill"><span class="fs-pill-icon">🏷️</span> White Label</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary-hero" href="/auth/register">Start Free — No Card</a>
        <a class="btn-ghost-hero" href="/pricing">View Pricing</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-subline">Free forever · Form your LLC → get 6 months Standard free · Cancel anytime</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 2 — Enterprise Speed / Edge Delivered
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="hero-slide slide-edge" data-slide="1" role="group" aria-label="Slide 2 of 4">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h1>Enterprise Speed.<br /><strong>Edge Delivered.</strong></h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">
        Insight Hunter runs in <strong>300+ cities worldwide</strong> — not in a single data center.
        Sub-50ms response time, zero cold starts, automatic DDoS protection, and data sovereignty controls.
        Zero infrastructure to manage. Ever.
      </p>

      <div class="edge-grid">
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">⚡</span><span class="ep-name">Workers</span><span class="ep-desc">Serverless Edge Functions</span></div>
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">🗄️</span><span class="ep-name">D1</span><span class="ep-desc">SQLite at the Edge</span></div>
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">📦</span><span class="ep-name">R2</span><span class="ep-desc">Zero-Egress Object Storage</span></div>
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">🤖</span><span class="ep-name">Workers AI</span><span class="ep-desc">On-Device Inference</span></div>
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">🔄</span><span class="ep-name">Durable Objects</span><span class="ep-desc">Stateful Coordination</span></div>
        <div class="edge-pill"><span class="ep-icon">🔁</span><span class="ep-name">Queues + Workflows</span><span class="ep-desc">Async Jobs</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary-hero" href="/auth/register">Start Free — No Card</a>
        <a class="btn-ghost-hero" href="/features">View Architecture</a>
      </div>
      <div class="edge-badges">
        <span>SOC 2 Ready</span><span>GDPR-Compliant</span>
        <span>99.99% uptime</span><span>No DevOps required</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 3 — Always Know Where You Stand
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="hero-slide slide-ai" data-slide="2" role="group" aria-label="Slide 3 of 4">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="slide-context-label">Financial intelligence — grounded in your actual books</span>
