      <p class="hero-sub">Nine purpose-built workers, each org-scoped and AI-powered.</p>

      <div class="platform-mini-grid">
        <div class="pmg-card">
          <span class="pmg-icon">📊</span>
          <span class="pmg-name">Dashboard</span>
          <span class="pmg-tier">All Plans</span>
          <p class="pmg-desc">Real-time P&L, KPI cards, cash flow. Always current.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pmg-card">
          <span class="pmg-icon">📒</span>
          <span class="pmg-name">Bookkeeping</span>
          <span class="pmg-tier">3 Tiers</span>
          <p class="pmg-desc">CSV import → full bank sync → automated reconciliation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pmg-card">
          <span class="pmg-icon">🔮</span>
          <span class="pmg-name">AI Forecasting</span>
