        </div>
        <div class="pmg-card">
          <span class="pmg-icon">📞</span>
          <span class="pmg-name">PBX</span>
          <span class="pmg-tier">Pro · Add-on</span>
          <p class="pmg-desc">IVR, call routing, voicemail transcription via Twilio.</p>
        </div>
